abstract.para:
Describes prerequisites you need to test the push messaging-enabled &AMHlong;
                    quickstart app in Android Studio, and send it a push notification using
                    &SNS;.

section.para:
We assume that you have already generated the quickstart app code using the &AMHlong;
            console, downloaded the code to your computer, built the project in Android Studio, and
            created a virtual device.

abstract.para:
Lists the steps you need to test the push messaging-enabled &AMHlong;
                    quickstart app in Android Studio, and send it a push notification using
                    &SNS;.

section.para:
After you successfully receive the test notifications, we recommend that you browse
            the &AMHlong; quickstart code so that you can see how the app interacts with &GCM;
            (&GCMlong;) and &SNS;.
